method.name: IsInitialized
method.comment: Tests whether the object has been initialized.

method.name: _clearformdata
method.comment: Clears any saved data for web forms. Added in API level 1. Deprecated in API level 26.

method.name: _clearhttpauthusernamepassword
method.comment: Clears any saved credentials for HTTP authentication. This method only clears the username and password stored in WebViewDatabase instance. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _clearusernamepassword
method.comment: Clears any saved username/password pairs for web forms. Note that these are unrelated to HTTP authentication credentials. Added in API level 1. Deprecated in API level 18.

method.name: _gethasformdata
method.comment: Gets whether there is any saved data for web forms. Added in API level 1. Deprecated in API level 26.

method.name: _gethashttpauthusernamepassword
method.comment: Gets whether there are any saved credentials for HTTP authentication. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _gethasusernamepassword
method.comment: Gets whether there are any saved username/password pairs for web forms. Note that these are unrelated to HTTP authentication credentials. Added in API level 1. Deprecated in API level 18.

method.name: _gethttpauthusernamepassword
method.comment: Retrieves HTTP authentication credentials for a given host and realm from the WebViewDatabase instance. Added in API level 26.

method.name: _initialize
method.comment: Initializes new instance of android.webkit.WebViewDatabase as WebkitWebViewDatabase for B4A. Added in API level 1.

method.name: _sethttpauthusernamepassword
method.comment: Stores HTTP authentication credentials for a given host and realm to the WebViewDatabase instance. Added in API level 26.

property.name: _hasformdata
property.comment: Gets whether there is any saved data for web forms. Added in API level 1. Deprecated in API level 26.

property.name: _hashttpauthusernamepassword
property.comment: Gets whether there are any saved credentials for HTTP authentication. Added in API level 1.

property.name: _hasusernamepassword
property.comment: Gets whether there are any saved username/password pairs for web forms. Note that these are unrelated to HTTP authentication credentials. Added in API level 1. Deprecated in API level 18.
